  "id": "RAW_eb677fcc",
  "title": "深势科技获 8 亿融资：做 AI for Science 的“安卓系统”",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&mid=2247622688&idx=2&sn=537a07a16c08500b155e01c6ae06349a",
  "date": "2025-12-26 02:10:00",
  "author": "硅星人Pro",
  "siteName": "硅星人Pro",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 30px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;background:none;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"562\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100138955\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e99a756c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FjopKOlhibRBKVsvFtpbjsa9H8Oicpf5DtEuxnNk97LK6OCycqt9ibkibr2xgG5oZGxntpPibKBv4tsVvqLIvIHuaB7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 15px 0px 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-size: 13px;line-height: 21px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者</span><i style=\"letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></i><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Yoky</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><span leaf=\"\">邮箱</span><i style=\"letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></i><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">yokyliu@pingwest.com</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">站在2025年的岁末回望，AI for Science（AI4S）已彻底告别了实验室里的‘概念验证’阶段，甚至</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">跃升为全球科技巨头竞相角逐的下一个战略主战场。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">英伟达正在试图将其芯片与CUDA生态变成科学计算的“操作系统”，不仅涉足气候预测（Earth-2），更通过NIM微服务嵌入生物医药工作流；微软则通过MatterGen和TRAIN联盟，在材料与医疗领域构建“生成—验证”的闭环标准；谷歌DeepMind更是凭借GNoME一次性解锁了相当于人类800年实验产出的新晶体结构。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">在硅谷，这已经是一个巨头环伺的赛道。</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">但在中国，行业格局却呈现出另一种张力：科技巨头尚未完全关注这一垂直领域，市场的“生态真空”为具备全栈能力的创业公司预留了成长为平台级企业的珍贵窗口。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">不同于单纯追求模型参数的竞赛，深势科技</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">（</span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">DP&nbsp;</span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Technology</span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">）</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">选择了一条更务实的路径：做“科学发现的基建工”。它试图在底层算力和上层应用之间，搭建一套通用的操作系统，让复杂的科学</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">探索</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">变得像使用手机App一样简单。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">近日，深势科技完成总额超8亿人民币的C轮融资，本轮融资由达晨</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">财</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">智</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">、京国瑞基金、北京市人工智能产业投资基金、北京市医药健康产业投资基金、联想创投、元禾璞华等机构共同出资。在资本趋于冷静的当下，这笔巨额融资不仅是金额惊人，更是一个明确的行业信号：</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">资本市场正在从投资“单点技术的突破”，转向投资“科学发现的工业化基础设施”</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一部分：不仅是工具，而是做科学界的“安卓”</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">在2025年AI for Science（AI4S）的赛道上，我们观察到一个显著的战略分化。绝大多数公司选择的是“做深”。它们或专注于攻克蛋白质折叠的单一难题，或深耕某一种特定新材料的生成。这种“小而美”的垂直路径固然能带来单点突破，却极易陷入无法通用化和规模化的泥潭，最终沦为大型药企或化工巨头的技术外包商。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">深势科技的选择截然不同。这家由“北大元培90后”创立的独角兽企业，从第一天起就没有把自己定义为一家单纯的软件开发商，而是试图构建一个“生态系统”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">正如创始人张林峰所言，AI for Science不只是一条新兴赛道，而是一项面向未来几十年科学发现的基础设施建设工程。在国家将“人工智能+科学研究”放在首位的大背景下，资本投下的，是对抗全球科技竞争中“卡脖子”风险的确定性，也是对从“</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">经验</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">试错</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">”向“</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">智能</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">设计”转型的必然性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">与DeepMind专注于攻克一个个“诺奖级”难题（如AlphaFold 3或GNoME）略有不同，深势科技在中国独特的产业土壤中，摸索出了一条更具生态粘性的路径：做“科学界的安卓”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就好比智能手机时代，不仅需要好用的App，更需要一个强大的操作系统（OS）来调度底层硬件与上层应用。深势科技正在构建的，正是这样一套从底层模型到上层应用，再到开发者生态的完整“三级火箭”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">安卓系统的核心在于Linux内核对硬件资源的调度，而深势科技的“内核”，则是其全面升级的“深势·宇知”科学发现智能引擎。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">不同于ChatGPT学习人类语言的概率分布，“深势·宇知”学习的是</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">微观世界</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">的</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">物理规律</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。它包含了一系列硬核的预训练模型，如专注于分子构象的</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Uni-Mol</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">和解决行业痛点“维数灾难”的</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">DPA</span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">原子</span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">大模型</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于强大的内核，深势科技构建了一个名为“玻尔·科研空间站”的产品矩阵。这相当于应用商店里的核心App，通过</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">一种</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">被</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">重新</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">定义的</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">“</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">SaaS</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">”</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">模式</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">（Science as a Service）</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，将复杂的科学计算变成了标准化的工业软件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，为了打通“读—算—做”的闭环，深势</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">致力于将纷繁复杂的实验设备统一管控</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">已</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Uni-Lab OS</span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">整合接入</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">了100多款高频</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用的</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">实验仪器。这意味着，AI不仅能在云端计算，还能指挥现实中的机械臂做实验，真正实现了研发的自动化。</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"340\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100138953\" data-ratio=\"0.6053333333333333\" width=\"1650\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"998\" style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;width:100%;display:block;letter-spacing:inherit;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8aec0bf0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjopKOlhibRBKVsvFtpbjsa9H8Oicpf5DtECJxhQOicjyPicTmC51XNib2ATWdmn9kfzqB5LCHuGk23uIWd7iaHsAZbibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">最关键的是，</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">深势</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">成熟的</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">开源</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">开放生态</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">凭借</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">其</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">打造的</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">玻尔</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">·</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">科研空间</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">站</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">已</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">服务</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">了全球</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">超过</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">1000</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">所高校的300多万科学家。张林峰曾深刻地指出，开源社区的本质是从一个“弱连接的社区形态”向“开放开发系统”的进化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统的科研软件公司</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，往往是卖出一套软件就结束了，用户是孤立的。深势则是让全世界的科学家习惯在这个系统上开发新的算法、上传新的模型。每一个新用户的加入，都在为平台贡献数据和反馈，从而反哺底层的“宇知”大模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种模式建立了极强的壁垒。它不是在卖单一的“铲子”，而是在建立一个生态。当全球最聪明的头脑都习惯用Bohrium跑数据、用Uni-Mol做预测时，深势就掌握了未来科学发现的入口。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二部分：跑通了AI4S的经济模型</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">在科技创新浪潮中，一个项目的价值评估正经历深刻转向。当深势科技完成8亿元融资，市场关注的焦点已非单纯的“技术炫酷”，而在于其能否精准切入产业核心痛点，并带来可量化的经济回报。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这标志着AI for Science（AI4S）的价值逻辑已完成关键闭环：从辅助科研的“叙事工具”，演进为对抗研发成本指数级增长的&nbsp;</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">“新一代工业底座”</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。其商业含金量的内核，在于成功将物理学的突破，转化为一本清晰可算的“经济账”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统工业研发，尤其在生物医药、新材料、新能源等领域，长期受困于一个底层物理学魔咒：</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">“维数灾难”</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。它如同悬在创新之上的达摩克利斯之剑，锁死了效率与成本的极限。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">深势科技首席科学家张林峰对此有深刻解读：在微观尺度模拟原子、分子的行为时，系统的复杂程度（即“维数”）随原子数量增加而暴增，所需计算资源和数据量呈</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">指数级爆炸</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。例如，计算十几个原子的体系或许可行，但当面对真实场景中涉及数万原子的蛋白质，或需模拟溶液中成千上万分子的相互作用时，即便动用顶级超算，也算力竭尽、时间漫长。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">其直接商业后果是灾难性的：因为“算不动”，研发不得不高度依赖反复的“湿实验”试错。这种模式如同在黑暗迷宫中盲目摸索，不仅代价高昂：催生了新药研发“十年十亿美金”的经典困局，更导致新材料开发周期漫长，严重滞后于市场迭代需求。整个产业的创新效率，被禁锢在物理规律设定的天花板之下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">深势科技的商业价值基石，在于用“AI+物理”的方案，实现了对“维数灾难”的釜底抽薪。其核心并非简单用AI拟合数据，而是让AI深度学习和复现量子力学的底层物理规律（如势能函数），从而在保持第一性原理精度的前提下，将计算效率提升</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">数个数量级</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"311\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100138954\" data-ratio=\"0.5533333333333333\" width=\"2074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"1148\" style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;width:100%;display:block;letter-spacing:inherit;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9f4eff78&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjopKOlhibRBKVsvFtpbjsa9H8Oicpf5DtE6ibStUa3hKmsglicCIOGw2MyqeT85k83ybtnibPucR8S3MnIovXFcgMVw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这不仅是科学突破，更是一场商业上的&nbsp;</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">“时间折叠”</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;。一个极具说服力的案例是：此前，科研人员为精确模拟</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">64个水分子</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">的微观相互作用，需消耗顶级超算2亿核时，耗时</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">三个月</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，仅机时成本便堪比天价。而今，基于深势科技的DPA预训练大模型，同一任务在</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">一台普通笔记本电脑</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">上，仅需</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">不到五天</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">即可完成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术的降维打击，最终必须转化为客户账本上清晰的</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">降本增效</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。深势科技交出的答卷，将其技术叙事扎实地锚定在经济叙事之上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">最直接的体现是成本结构的重塑。根据合作伙伴的实测反馈，在引入深势的AI计算平台后，研发中对昂贵、耗时的湿实验依赖程度大幅降低，相关成本平均下降高达</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">76%</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。与此同时，该平台已助力合作伙伴沉淀了超过</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">50项</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">经过计算验证的高价值科学资产（如先导化合物、新材料配方），这些数字资产构成了未来持续创新的核心资本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">翰森制药、复星医药</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">等药企而言，这意味着药物发现从“大海捞针”的运气游戏，转向“按图索骥”的理性设计。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">深势的Uni-Fold是全球首个最快复现Alphafold的工作，且在Alphafold3发布时被列为了排名第一的benchmark。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">宁德时代、比亚迪</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">等新能源巨头，该技术能以前所未有的速度筛选高性能电解液、正负极材料，成为在激烈技术军备竞赛中抢得先机的关键利器。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">当一家公司能够帮助客户将研发过程中的“运气”成分转化为可重复、可预测的“计算”过程，将“十年磨一剑”的漫长周期压缩为“数年出成果”的敏捷节奏，它的价值便深深嵌入了客户的核心价值链与竞争力之中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这正是资本市场给予深势科技高估值的根本逻辑：它正将</span></span><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">不可预测的科学发现，转变为一门可计算、可规划、可预期的高确定性生意</span></span></b><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。这8亿元融资，不仅是对其技术领先性的认可，更是对这套已通过验证的“技术-经济”新范式的重磅投资。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "深势科技获 8 亿融资，以“AI+物理”构建 AI 加速科学发现的底层基础设施，旨在成为“科学界的安卓系统”，解决了“维数灾难”并实现了研发的显著降本增效。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "深势科技获 8 亿融资，以“AI+物理”构建 AI 加速科学发现的底层基础设施，旨在成为“科学界的安卓系统”，解决了“维数灾难”并实现了研发的显著降本增效。",
  "summary": "文章详细报道了深势科技完成超 8 亿元 C 轮融资的消息，并对其在 AI for Science（AI4S）领域的战略定位和商业模式进行了深度解析。深势科技选择了一条独特路径，致力于打造 AI for Science 领域的“安卓系统”，即从底层模型（如“深势·宇知”智能引擎及 Uni-Mol、DPA 原子大模型）到上层应用（如“玻尔·科研空间站”SaaS），再到开发者生态的完整基础设施。文章指出，深势科技的核心价值在于通过“AI+物理”的方法，有效解决了传统科学研发中“维数灾难”导致的效率低下和成本高昂问题，实现了计算效率的数个数量级提升，从而为生物医药、新材料等行业带来显著的降本增效，将科学发现从“运气游戏”转变为“可计算、可规划、可预期的高确定性生意”。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "深势科技致力于构建 AI for Science 领域的通用操作系统，即“科学界的安卓”。",
      "explanation": "区别于其他公司专注于单一难题或垂直领域，深势科技选择打造从底层科学智能引擎、标准化工业 SaaS 到开放开发者生态的“三级火箭”式基础设施。"
    },
    {
      "point": "核心技术通过“AI+物理”解决“维数灾难”问题，显著提升科学计算效率。",
      "explanation": "其“深势·宇知”智能引擎包含 Uni-Mol 和 DPA 原子大模型，学习微观物理规律，能在保持量子力学精度的前提下，将计算效率提升数个数量级，大幅缩短研发周期。"
    },
    {
      "point": "商业模式实现了 AI4S 的经济闭环，将科研成果转化为可量化的降本增效。",
      "explanation": "通过减少对昂贵“湿实验”的依赖，平均降低 76%的研发成本，并沉淀高价值科学资产，将科学发现从不确定性转化为可预测的商业价值，获得资本市场认可。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过构建开放生态和社区，形成了强大的护城河与用户粘性。",
      "explanation": "“玻尔·科研空间站”服务全球科学家，并通过 Uni-Lab OS 整合实验仪器，实现了研发的自动化闭环。用户使用平台贡献数据和反馈，反哺底层模型，形成飞轮效应。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "在资本趋于冷静的当下，这笔巨额融资不仅是金额惊人，更是一个明确的行业信号：资本市场正在从投资“单点技术的突破”，转向投资“科学发现的工业化基础设施”。",
    "深势科技的选择截然不同。这家由“北大元培 90 后”创立的独角兽企业，从第一天起就没有把自己定义为一家单纯的软件开发商，而是试图构建一个“生态系统”。",
    "深势科技的商业价值基石，在于用“AI+物理”的方案，实现了对“维数灾难”的釜底抽薪。",
